game.name: First Day At College
game.description:
Anna and Moana put their best efforts no matter what they do in their normal and regular life. Today is the first day of their college and they want to make it special with their unique and trendy looks. So they need some cool outfits for this purpose. But it is not going to be easy at all since they also have to undergo the ragging managed by their senior batch of students. Help your girls first to find out the hidden items and then dress them up in Anna And Moana College Girls!

First of all, join your girls in their class and guide them to find out all the hidden items in this HTML5 hidden game. The bottom part of the screen will show you how many items you will have to find out. All you need to do is just click on them to perform the hidden task successfully. There will be glasses, backpacks, stapler, mobile phone, headphone, and sharpener. Once you find everything you need for a class in college, go to help them to pick up the college outfits. 

Start with Anna by dressing her up with the cool outfit in this awesome fun dressing game! Give her a purple lace t-shirt and combine it with a black skirt with some pink rose prints! Make sure to pair her dress with nice hairstyle, denim jacket, a pink headband and a blue scarf. Dress up Moana with a black t-shirt along with a pair of matching red jeans! A small black bag, and a pink cap, ponytail hairstyle can help to complete her look. Good luck to create the best outfits for other popular characters in our other college and school games!
